body:
I messaged support almost 2 years ago regarding the kindred figure, i asked for it to be restocked, then over a year later still nothing. then you decide to retire it? Why retire something that people actually want to purchase? I cant find it anywhere, ebay, amazon, facebook. Why Retire something that people want? retire the stuff no one wants like coasters...

I feel its really disappointing riot missed this. multiple tickets in, saying they dont know when it will be restocked, to look and see its retired... come on.. a massive company, constantly putting out new merch but couldnt put out another restock? 

